nbc might have flopped with its nurse drama 
nightingales but its summer nurse comedy 13 east finished 
in the top 10 helping the network win another nielsen ratings 
derby victory 
for the week ended july 30 nbcs cheers landed in first 
place for the fourth time in five weeks narrowly topping abcs 
roseanne cheers had a rating of 175 only onetenth of a 
point ahead of roseanne 
last week they tied for first place at 174 
nbc easily won the week for its 58th straight victory in the 
ac nielsen co survey the only surprise in the top 10 was the 
appearance of lightly regarded 13 east which finished 10th 
other than cbs 60 minutes and murder she wrote all 
the shows in the top 10 were comedies 
the ratings are certainly proof of the resurgence of the 
situation comedy which was all but written off a few years ago 
primetime soap operas like dallas and dynasty dominated 
the ratings until the appearance of the cosby show in 1984 in 
the 198384 season the only comedy in the top 10 was cbs kate amp 
allie 
comedy also dominated the second 10 highestrated shows this 
past week with seven entries 
here are the top 10 nbcs cheers abcs roseanne nbcs 
the cosby show nbcs a different world nbcs dear 
john nbcs the golden girls and cbs 60 minutes tied 
cbs murder she wrote abcs the wonder years and nbcs 
13 east 
fox broadcasting continued its summer surge in the ratings 
married with children was in 29th place americas most 
wanted was tied for 34th and totally hidden video was tied 
for 39th place 
nbc was first with an average of 108 cbs was second with 89 
and abc was third with 87 the averages since the fall season 
began on sept 19 were nbc 148 abc 119 and cbs 118 
the ratings is the percentage of the estimated 904 million 
homes in the united states with television the share is the 
percentage of sets in use 
the nbc summer show knight and daye did not fare that well 
in the ratings it was in 37th place 
the lowestrated show on the three networks was cbs american 
nuclear here are the bottom five cbs tour of duty nbcs 
jim henson abcs nick and frankie abcs 
transantarctica expedition and cbs american nuclear 
