charged with creating a mechanism for monitoring the pullout of 
vietnamese troops 
hun sen has said the vietnamese forces in his country have 
already been reduced to 26000 vietnam has said it will pull out 
the last of those troops once estimated at more than 50000 by 
sept 27 
it was still unclear however when the un team would leave 
for cambodia and whether the khmer rouge would make the 
unprecedented gesture of allowing the mission to visit the refugee 
camps it controls 
the khmer rouge killed an estimated 1 million people with its 
harsh programs after it drove out a usbacked government and took 
power in 1975 
the groups role in a future government has been a sticking 
point at the conference 
hun sen says the chinesebacked khmer rouge should be destroyed 
china says the khmer rouge should take part in a transitional 
government 
