energy and commerce committee also is looking into kellys 
allegations the staffer speaking on condition of anonymity also 
said the justice department is investigating 
air force sgt michael grinnell spokesman in washington for the 
air force investigations office said i can confirm that we do 
have an ongoing investigation concerning mischarging of facility 
repair costs for leased buildings by mischarging we mean 
overcharging doublebilling 
kelly said that when boeing went to repair some of the problems 
it had to fix some of them a second or third time im told by 
the afosi that the taxpayers pay for all of these repairs not 
sabey 
